@startuml

left to right direction

' === ACTORS ===

actor User
actor Administrator
actor System as "Background System"

' === FRONTEND DASHBOARD USE CASES ===

rectangle "Frontend Dashboard" {

  ' Dashboard home/overview
  (View Dashboard Home) as UC1
  (View Opportunity Overview) as UC2
  (View Best Deals) as UC3
  (View Price Trends) as UC4

  ' Opportunity browser
  (Browse Opportunities) as UC5
  (Search Opportunities) as UC6
  (Filter Opportunities) as UC7
  (Sort Table) as UC8
  (View Opportunity Details) as UC9
  (Export Opportunities) as UC10

  ' Analytics
  (View Analytics) as UC11
  (View Discount Distribution) as UC12
  (View Market Trends) as UC13
  (View Top Brands) as UC14
  (View Marketplace Comparison) as UC15

  ' Settings
  (Configure Settings) as UC16
  (Configure Scraping Schedule) as UC17
  (Configure Alert Thresholds) as UC18
  (Toggle Marketplace Sources) as UC19
  (Configure Discount Filters) as UC20

  ' Monitoring
  (View Monitoring) as UC21
  (View Scrape Status) as UC22
  (View API Health) as UC23
  (View Message Queue) as UC24

  ' Historical
  (View Historical Data) as UC25
  (View Archived Opportunities) as UC26
  (View Price Evolution) as UC27
  (Export Historical Data) as UC28
}

' === USER INTERACTIONS ===

User --> UC1 : access home
UC1 ..> UC2 : <<include>>
UC1 ..> UC3 : <<include>>
UC1 ..> UC4 : <<include>>

User --> UC5 : browse
UC5 ..> UC6 : <<extend>>
UC5 ..> UC7 : <<extend>>
UC5 ..> UC8 : <<extend>>
User --> UC9 : view details
UC5 --> UC9 : from table

User --> UC10 : export

User --> UC11 : view analytics
UC11 ..> UC12 : <<include>>
UC11 ..> UC13 : <<include>>
UC11 ..> UC14 : <<include>>
UC11 ..> UC15 : <<include>>

Administrator --> UC16 : configure
UC16 ..> UC17 : <<include>>
UC16 ..> UC18 : <<include>>
UC16 ..> UC19 : <<include>>
UC16 ..> UC20 : <<include>>

Administrator --> UC21 : monitor
UC21 ..> UC22 : <<include>>
UC21 ..> UC23 : <<include>>
UC21 ..> UC24 : <<include>>

User --> UC25 : view history
UC25 ..> UC26 : <<extend>>
UC25 ..> UC27 : <<extend>>
UC25 --> UC28 : export

' === SYSTEM INTERACTIONS ===

System --> UC2 : provides metrics
System --> UC3 : provides top deals
System --> UC4 : provides price data
System --> UC5 : provides opportunity data
System --> UC11 : provides analytics data
System --> UC21 : provides system status
System --> UC22 : provides scrape logs

note bottom of User
  Standard user viewing
  opportunities and analytics
end note

note bottom of Administrator
  Admin configuring system
  and monitoring health
end note

note bottom of System
  FIPE Hunter backend
  providing data via API
end note

@enduml
